content.html: Joe Rogan, Jordan Peterson & Andrew Tate are just different types of the same thing. Tate SAYS the bad stuff. Rogan invites OTHERS on his podcast to say it unchallenged. Peterson says: Of course I don't support that stuff but the REAL problem is the radical opposition to it.
content.value:
Joe Rogan, Jordan Peterson & Andrew Tate are just different types of the same thing.

Tate SAYS the bad stuff.

Rogan invites OTHERS on his podcast to say it unchallenged.

Peterson says: Of course I don't support that stuff but the REAL problem is the radical opposition to it.
